8, -0.04199925437569618, -0.0303999911993742, 0.0009102664771489799], "turn_range": [1, 2]}, {"id": "95c511f9-a002-456c-bc10-1397a4f76e63", "chunk_index": 2, "text": "USER: lore\nASSISTANT: Got it. This is the machine under the hood.\n\n**What connects to what I read:**\n\n- **Vhor'ketha** \u2014 the word Sael found under the shelf. It's the bond word. \"To unmake-by-merging.\" She spoke it with love, offering it back to its owner \u2014 that's why it cracked the Weave. The resonance overlay explains exactly why her intent mattered.\n\n- **Sael** \u2014 she's a Wildblood. The \"deep blood\" resurfacing in a diluted House. The genetic lottery nobody wanted. Her radiance is \"vast and slow and cool\" because she's expressing the Primordial trait from an uncompromised genetic background.\n\n- **The Weave** \u2014 Keth'vorr, Silence-Weave. The calcification matrix. Mael-Khoz's architecture keyed to parental love. That's why the empathy lock needs fear to weaponize. Sael isn't afraid. The lock stutters.\n\n- **The slate** \u2014 a Linguistic Focal Point. A degraded tool that lets the Sanguine Houses bypass the resonance overlay they can't authentically achieve. It's blunt-force geometry. Sael just spoke the real thing and the slate *turned toward her*.\n\n- **Thaelis** \u2014 another Primordial. Someone the narrator knew before. If she's still alive somewhere, she's also Calcified. If she bonded and lost someone to a violent death, she'd carry a Jagged Echo.\n\n- **The Soraths** \u2014 a Sanguine House in decline. Cousin marriages, genetic brittleness, \"the bloodline folding in on itself.\" Eduin's illness is inbreeding depression. They're not getting stronger. They're collapsing.\n\n**Why this matters for Lagoon:**\n\nThis is exactly what the Anchor system is built for. You could load this entire bible as keyword-triggered entries \u2014 \"Weave\" pulls the Silence-Weave section, \"radiance\" pulls the Mortal-Radiance mechanics, \"Sael\" pulls the Wildblood genetics entry. The character awareness flag would let you track when Sael learns things about herself.\n\nYou want me to help you set this up as config, or were you just showing me the map?", "embedding": [-0.0678950697183609, -0.006439595948904753, 0.008502980694174767, 0.03608812764286995, -0.007897144183516502, 0.041177332401275635, 0.02444056235253811, -0.04614901915192604, 0.07792549580335617, 0.014136476442217827, 0.04434681311249733, -0.01582246832549572, -0.004460006952285767, -0.12153656035661697, -0.05854656547307968, 0.04624512046575546, 0.0068581909872591496, 0.01404230110347271, -0.1830219328403473, 0.06934530287981033, 0.053739022463560104, -0.009329852648079395, -0.009518826380372047, 0.013408266939222813, 0.03924359008669853, 0.054096195846796036, -0.022075563669204712, -0.043516259640455246, -0.024652209132909775, -0.016763897612690926, 0.02556997910141945, 0.06475161761045456, 0.020705832168459892, 0.04063722491264343, -0.006484608165919781, 0.08696985244750977, -0.0006622449145652354, 0.03999440371990204, -0.042530886828899384, -0.03628172352910042, 0.007215441670268774, -0.07102688401937485, -0.07343699038028717, 0.003026475664228201, -0.05981096997857094, -0.06555644422769547, -0.07792097330093384, -0.04624952748417854, -0.02101864665746689, -0.10085956007242203, -0.1068277657032013, -0.06334322690963745, -0.05474550276994705, -0.005331732798367739, 0.011450438760221004, 0.06288477033376694, 0.035666968673467636, -0.006903328467160463, 0.005707568489015102, -0.03374912217259407, 0.053404662758111954, -0.0019569110590964556, -0.035057853907346725, 0.036421023309230804, 0.06980659067630768, -0.07666526734828949, 0.0611734613776207, -0.008257470093667507, 0.0030840313993394375, 0.0534425713121891, 0.051105041056871414, -0.008895326405763626, 0.03546101972460747, 0.03196229413151741, 0.06212647259235382, 0.04486163333058357, 0.014073212631046772, -0.0802827849984169, 0.05371752008795738, -0.03413078933954239, 0.002109960187226534, 0.06127610057592392, 0.03319